{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you had to have-- they called it [NON-ENGLISH], you know, who is behind, and there was always a gentile-- to carry on with his-- this other business he was doing, like kitchenware and--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, the business didn't take off for the simple reason because there was no goods available.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't buy anything-- a shortage in everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went up to-- no, we went up to Budapest in 1941.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the pressure came on us very well with all the others-- the relatives and also in the Chinese.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brothers-- we'll come back to this later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were there-- were there any restrictions on Jews in Budapest?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same-- everywhere restriction-- but in Budapest, sort of you could go by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was such a large Jewish city, I would say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you-- you get lost in the-- in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you see, when some regulation comes, and it's in Fil'akovo, everybody knows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If a regulation comes in Budapest, you know, I mean, nothing-- And what regulations were imposed on you in Budapest?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What kind of things were you restricted from doing?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't have your own business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't study.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were numerous clauses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, in Hungary, really those-- those anti-Jewish regulation goes back till [NON-ENGLISH], which was, you know, still believed in a-- in a democracy in-- in-- in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was already started to have the numerous clauses in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to live there and to readjust, it was the last one sort of to be in those-- the destruction of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- we managed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Really, it wasn't difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, my mother tongue is Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
